Add `opentelemetry-instrumentation-alephalpha`, instrumenting the
`aleph_alpha_client` Python SDK text completions (`Client.complete` /
`AsyncClient.complete`), emitting standard GenAI semantic conventions
(`gen_ai.*`) via `opentelemetry-util-genai`. Requires
`OTEL_SEMCONV_STABILITY_OPT_IN=gen_ai_latest_experimental`.
